cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.WEB 

This paper deals with web crawling and analyzing web data, which falls under the categories of digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and web search (cs.WEB). The paper also discusses the use of persistent identifiers (PIDs), which are commonly used in computer security (cs.CR) and system and information theory (cs.SI).
